snippet.title: Sleepwalker gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Sleepwalker, Dos PC game produced by Ocean in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/sleepwalker/665/
It's night and all people sleep in town but not a young kid... and his dog to help him finding the way to bed.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Fury of the Furries - https://youtu.be/gitjMDoJPZs
Mission: Impossible - https://youtu.be/lGLckisXL0c
Drak - https://youtu.be/n1en65Ip5NI
